{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-timeline-js","path":"/tiimgreen/github-cheat-sheet/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"awesomeList":{"repo":"tiimgreen/github-cheat-sheet","descriptionHTML":"<div>A list of cool features of Git and GitHub.</div>","description":"A list of cool features of Git and GitHub."},"awesomeListMeta":{"readmeParsedAt":"2021-06-27T23:26:58.087Z"},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Pressing <code>s</code> will focus the search field for the current repository. Pressing ↓ to select the “All GitHub” option changes the field to search all of GitHub.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-02-02T15:41:57.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Pressing <code>y</code> <strong>when looking at a file</strong> (e.g., <code>https://github.com/tiimgreen/github-cheat-sheet/blob/master/README.md</code>) will change your URL to one which, in effect, freezes the page you are looking at. If this code changes, you will still be able to see what you saw at that current time.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-08T16:35:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Git Grep</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>-e</code> The next parameter is the pattern (e.g., regex)</li>","updatedAt":"2016-09-08T16:35:38.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Empty Commits</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>The first commit of a repository: <code>git commit -m \"Initial commit\" --allow-empty</code>.</li>","updatedAt":"2016-02-07T16:59:58.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Git Grep</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>--and</code>, <code>--or</code> and <code>--not</code> Combine multiple patterns.</li>","updatedAt":"2015-06-03T20:06:56.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Emojis</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>:shipit:</code></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-21T00:31:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Emojis</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>:sparkles:</code></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-21T00:31:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Emojis</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>:-1:</code></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-21T00:31:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Emojis</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>:+1:</code></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-21T00:31:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Emojis</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><code>:clap:</code></li>","updatedAt":"2015-01-21T00:31:45.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h4>Task Lists in Markdown Documents</h4>","itemHTML":"<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> Venus</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-28T18:16:07.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h4>Task Lists in Markdown Documents</h4>","itemHTML":"<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Mercury</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-28T18:15:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h4>Task Lists in Markdown Documents</h4>","itemHTML":"<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> Earth\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> Moon</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-28T18:15:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h4>Task Lists in Markdown Documents</h4>","itemHTML":"<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" checked disabled> Mars\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Deimos</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled> Phobos</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-28T18:15:16.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Stripspace</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Strips trailing whitespace</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-16T17:09:35.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Stripspace</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Collapses newlines</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-16T17:09:35.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Stripspace</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Adds newline to end of file</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-16T17:09:35.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Empty Commits</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Annotating the start of a new bulk of work or a new feature.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-14T19:04:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Empty Commits</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Documenting when you make changes to the project that aren't code related.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-14T19:04:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Git</h2><h3>Empty Commits</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Communicating with people using your repository.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-14T19:04:18.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Pressing <code>t</code> will bring up a file explorer.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-14T18:49:22.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Pressing <code>w</code> will bring up the branch selector.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-14T18:49:22.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>GitHub</h2><h3>Keyboard Shortcuts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>Pressing <code>l</code> will edit labels on existing Issues.</li>","updatedAt":"2014-04-14T18:49:22.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/stefanbuck/awesome-browser-extensions-for-github","repo":"stefanbuck/awesome-browser-extensions-for-github"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/matchai/awesome-pinned-gists","repo":"matchai/awesome-pinned-gists"}},"pageContext":{"repo":"tiimgreen/github-cheat-sheet","id":"awesomes/github.com/tiimgreen/github-cheat-sheet","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/stefanbuck/awesome-browser-extensions-for-github","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/matchai/awesome-pinned-gists"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","3289010534"]}